textBox.richText: Gingerbread houses, usually thought of as for Christmas, but apparently not. Since I had to house sit for my parents, and since there is NOTHING to do on Long Island, Kelly made me buy a gingerbread house and have US put it together. The reason I put emphasis on US is because, I held the pieces together while she essentially did the rest. My supervisor skills came into use that day, and alas you can see my....AHEM....I mean our accomplishment.
THINGS KELLY likes to do when we are bored
